text: Zafra is a city in Badajoz, Spain. Zafra may also refer to: *Zafra (agriculture), harvest time, especially that of sugar in the Spanish-speaking Caribbean *Zafra (film), a 1958 Argentine film *Zafra (gastropod), a gastropod genus in the family Columbellidae *Zafra (human), that one guy I know named Zafra
